        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "For most file change events in your vault, the plugin's database is kept in sync automatically. However, some vault changes don't remove plugin data immediately to avoid expensive LLM API calls in case it's needed again (such as building embeddings). This button manually prunes the plugin database.",
